### 冷藏集装箱异常通知服务 API 测试文件

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### 1. 查询告警规则列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/alert-rules?enabled=true
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 按货类查询规则 (疫苗 VACCINE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/alert-rules?cargoType=VACCINE
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 创建设备数据上报 - 疫苗箱温度异常 (应触发告警)
POST {{baseUrl}}/device-data/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "containerNo": "REEFER001",
  "temperature": 10.5,
  "humidity": 45,
  "doorOpen": false,
  "powerStatus": true,
  "latitude": 31.2304,
  "longitude": 121.4737,
  "speed": 65
}

### 4. 创建设备数据上报 - 疫苗箱开门 (应触发告警)
POST {{baseUrl}}/device-data/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "containerNo": "REEFER001",
  "temperature": 5.0,
  "doorOpen": true,
  "powerStatus": true
}

### 5. 创建设备数据上报 - 冻品温度异常 (短时波动不应立即告警)
POST {{baseUrl}}/device-data/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "containerNo": "REEFER002",
  "temperature": -15.0,
  "humidity": 60,
  "doorOpen": false,
  "powerStatus": true
}

### 6. 创建设备数据上报 - 冻品开门 (短时开门不应告警)
POST {{baseUrl}}/device-data/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "containerNo": "REEFER002",
  "temperature": -20.0,
  "doorOpen": true,
  "powerStatus": true
}

### 7. 创建设备数据上报 - 断电告警
POST {{baseUrl}}/device-data/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "containerNo": "REEFER003",
  "temperature": 12.0,
  "powerStatus": false
}

### 8. 查询告警列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?status=ACTIVE
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. 获取告警统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts/stats
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. 查询通知列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. 提交处置回执 - 已确认
# 先从告警列表获取一个 alertId
POST {{baseUrl}}/receipts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alertId": "replace-with-alert-id",
  "handlerId": "13800138001",
  "handlerName": "张师傅",
  "status": "CONFIRMED",
  "remark": "已检查，正在处理"
}

### 12. 提交处置回执 - 误报
POST {{baseUrl}}/receipts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alertId": "replace-with-alert-id",
  "handlerId": "13800138002",
  "handlerName": "李调度",
  "status": "FALSE_ALARM",
  "remark": "传感器故障，已校准"
}

### 13. 提交处置回执 - 升级理赔
POST {{baseUrl}}/receipts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alertId": "replace-with-alert-id",
  "handlerId": "13800138003",
  "handlerName": "王客服",
  "status": "ESCALATED",
  "remark": "货物可能受损，申请理赔"
}

### 14. 查询回执列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/receipts
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. 手动触发通知发送
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/replace-with-alert-id/send
Content-Type: application/json

### 16. 手动升级告警
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/replace-with-alert-id/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

### 17. 创建设备数据 - 恢复正常 (告警应自动解决)
POST {{baseUrl}}/device-data/report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "containerNo": "REEFER001",
  "temperature": 5.0,
  "doorOpen": false,
  "powerStatus": true
}

### 18. 创建新的告警规则
POST {{baseUrl}}/alert-rules
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试规则-生鲜温度",
  "cargoType": "FRESH_PRODUCE",
  "alertType": "TEMPERATURE_HIGH",
  "alertLevel": "WARNING",
  "minValue": 0,
  "maxValue": 10,
  "allowedDuration": 300,
  "tolerance": 1,
  "description": "生鲜温度超过10℃，持续5分钟告警",
  "enabled": true
}
